# Holio Brand Rules

## Identity
- App name: "Holio Agent" (short: "Holio")
- NEVER use "Telegram", "Slack", "clone", or "copy" in any user-facing text
- Logo: Bold uppercase "HOLIO" wordmark in heavy geometric sans-serif (e.g. Black weight of Inter, Montserrat, or similar)

## Color Palette
- Primary Orange: `#FF9220` -- CTA buttons, active states, sent message bubbles, accent text
- Dark: `#152022` -- sidebar background, dark sections, dark mode base
- Lavender: `#D1CBFB` -- secondary surfaces, selected states, hover effects
- Sage Green: `#C6D5BA` -- tertiary accent, success states
- Off-white: `#FCFCF8` -- page backgrounds, panel backgrounds
- White: `#FFFFFF` -- cards, received message bubbles
- Text Dark: `#1A1A1A` -- primary text on light backgrounds
- Text Light: `#FFFFFF` -- text on dark backgrounds
- Text Muted: `#8E8E93` -- timestamps, secondary text

## Tailwind Config
When referencing these colors in Tailwind, use the custom palette names:
- `holio-orange`, `holio-dark`, `holio-lavender`, `holio-sage`, `holio-offwhite`

## Typography
- Headings: Bold/Black weight geometric sans-serif
- Body: Regular weight, 14-16px base
- Chat messages: 14px
- Timestamps: 12px, muted color

## Tone
- Professional but approachable
- Corporate-friendly, not casual
- Clean, modern, minimal UI chrome
